metadata.name: Web -3
metadata.description:
We are in a new paradigm.

The world is evolving. How we communicate and financially transact has totally changed.

This is a commemorative NFT for anyone who has ever rushed to mint on Metamask mobile, it has taken 5 minutes to load and the mint is finished by the time you hit the mint site.

As I said, its a new paradigm, in frustration.

This is art. There will be no project, no games, no puzzles or burn mechanisms. No discord, no twitter. Just an image to remind you of all the generational wealth you have missed due to this shit.
